Package: WeatherWhatever
Title: Weather Data Plotter
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bohan", "Fu", , "fubohan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The Weather Data Plotter is an application developed using R Shiny that allows users to plot historical weather data for any given city. Users can select a city by clicking on the map or entering by text, specify a date range, and visualize temperature and weather data over time.
